 *  down and left) directions and you can test for these individually by ANDing
 *  it with the corresponding direction.
 *
 *  @code
 *  if (hats[2] & GLFW_HAT_RIGHT)
 *  {
 *      // State of hat 2 could be right-up, right or right-down
 *  }
 *  @endcode
 *
